'''Gaza Weekly Newspaper''' is a weekly [[newspaper]] established in 1950, and published from the city of [[Gaza City|Gaza]]. The first issue was on 6 July 1951. The newspaper is printed in the Zeitoun neighbourhood in Gaza City. It has been dealing with local issues and is distributed in [[Jordan]], [[Saudi Arabia]] and [[Egypt]].
